    "As such, we can detect any single-qubit error over the state-injection process.",
    "Some remarks on state-injection procedures.",
    "We have presented state-injection protocols for several different codes for the errorsuppressed magic state we discussed in the main text.",
    "We argued that we can detect a single error that may occur in any of these protocols, such that we maintain the error suppression we have demonstrated in our experiment.",
